 class="Popover"><div id="null-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="null-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-shu-shu-13">筑sir</a></div></div></span></div><div class="AuthorInfo-detail"><div class="AuthorInfo-badge"><div class="RichText ztext AuthorInfo-badgeText">设计院庸俗画图匠。公众号：筑叔叔 </div></div></div></div></div><div class="AnswerItem-extraInfo"><span class="Voters"><button type="button" class="Button Button--plain">8 人<!-- -->赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="image" content=""/><meta itemProp="upvoteCount" content="8"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/28122440/answer/345290831"/><meta itemProp="dateCreated" content="2018-03-19T05:45:34.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-03-19T05:45:34.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="3"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">如果是施工图的设计说明，一般都有模板按照真实情况填写即可。不过看题目，应该是指建筑方案设计的说明怎么写？应该是有不少人有这样的困惑：有人明明费劲气力做了一个非常有意思的方案，做的时候想了很多细节或者创意，但是一到讲解方案或者写说明的时候，就是不能把这个方案淋漓尽致的表达出来，如鲠在喉。甚至明明别人的方案设计没你好，但是偏偏人家讲的好，就打动了评委或者甲方。其实很多时候，尤其是方案阶段，我觉得说明…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"