itemProp="author" itemscope="" itemType="http://schema.org/Person"><meta itemProp="name" content="筑sir"/><meta itemProp="image" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-cfd49b3e6ecf9056279f3efddb0906ad_s.jpg"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-shu-shu-13"/><meta itemProp="zhihu:followerCount"/><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-avatarWrapper"><div class="Popover"><div id="null-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="null-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-shu-shu-13"><img class="Avatar AuthorInfo-avatar" width="38" height="38" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-cfd49b3e6ecf9056279f3efddb0906ad_xs.jpg" srcSet="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-cfd49b3e6ecf9056279f3efddb0906ad_l.jpg 2x" alt="筑sir"/></a></div></div></span><div class="AuthorInfo-content"><div class="AuthorInfo-head"><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-name"><div class="Popover"><div id="null-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="null-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-shu-shu-13">筑sir</a></div></div></span></div><div class="AuthorInfo-detail"><div class="AuthorInfo-badge"><div class="RichText ztext AuthorInfo-badgeText">设计院庸俗画图匠。公众号：筑叔叔 </div></div></div></div></div><div class="AnswerItem-extraInfo"><span class="Voters"><button type="button" class="Button Button--plain">90 人<!-- -->赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="image" content=""/><meta itemProp="upvoteCount" content="90"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/22008850/answer/278683238"/><meta itemProp="dateCreated" content="2017-12-18T11:22:22.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2017-12-19T10:43:35.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="145"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">我来回答下吧，最根本的原因是思考问题的出发点不同，就我所知，设计院的结构、机电专业的人，都对于整个项目了解，相对建筑而言都过于狭窄，一般只专注自己专业的内容，对于他们来说什么是好的设计？那就是对于他们自己专业而言图纸好画的设计，后期好服务的设计。不仅仅是结构，各专业黑建筑总结下来的原因就是上述这句话~每一次出现冲突的原因都是因为修改造成图纸不便，让他们产生修改嫌麻烦。仅此而已，其他都是借口~ 什么…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->90</button><button aria-label="反对" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--down"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleDown" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M20.044 3H3.956C2.876 3 2 3.517 2 4.9c0 .326.087.533.236.896L10.216 19c.355.571.87 1.143 1.784 1.143s1.429-.572 1.784-1.143l7.98-13.204c.149-.363.236-.57.236-.896 0-1.386-.876-1.9-1.956-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-action Button--plain Button--withIcon Button--withLabel"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--Comment Button-zi" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1.2em"